<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I disagree - she does waste words overexplaining things. It&apos;s a rambling, repetitive, and unorganized book. Also, there are so many mispronunciations <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I disagree - she does waste words overexplaining things. It's a rambling, repetitive, and unorganized book. Also, there are so many mispronunciations of viruses and locations in the audiobook... it's cringy.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
