    <a title="Nick Black" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/655723-nick-black"><img alt="Nick Black" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1315018121p2/655723.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1120331594?book_show_action=true">Dec 01, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nick Black" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nick Black" href="/user/show/655723-nick-black">Nick Black</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140250916" href="/book/show/46722.The_Coming_Plague">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Nick by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/26746403-emily-bragg">Emily Bragg</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/655723-nick-black?shelf=borrowing-will-give-back">borrowing-will-give-back</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/655723-nick-black?shelf=she-blinded-me-with-science">she-blinded-me-with-science</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1120331594" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15411677262479102393">pretty good. certainly thorough. &quot;epidemic&quot; is tossed around pretty liberally -- if a fever burns out a south american village, does it make a sound? poor editing, with numerous phrases and sentences repeated verbatim and certain acronyms expanded not at all, on late use, or multiple times. i&apos;d like to have seen more on the virology and suppression of HIV and fewer tedious pages of stats and prediction histories. worth reading, though.</span>
  <span id="freeText15411677262479102393" style="display:none">pretty good. certainly thorough. "epidemic" is tossed around pretty liberally -- if a fever burns out a south american village, does it make a sound? poor editing, with numerous phrases and sentences repeated verbatim and certain acronyms expanded not at all, on late use, or multiple times. i'd like to have seen more on the virology and suppression of HIV and fewer tedious pages of stats and prediction histories. worth reading, though.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15411677262479102393" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
